你能够调用以下的API:
[['StockDataRetrieval.get_historical_data', {'name': 'StockDataRetrieval.get_historical_data', 'description': 'This function retrieves historical stock market data based on the specified market and duration.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'market', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The stock market to retrieve data from, e.g., US, UK.'}, {'name': 'duration', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The duration of historical data to retrieve, e.g., 5 years, 10 years.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'data', 'description': 'Historical stock market data for the specified duration.'}]}], ['ResearchPaperSearch.find_papers', {'name': 'ResearchPaperSearch.find_papers', 'description': 'This function searches for academic papers based on a topic, location, and count.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'topic', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The topic of the academic papers, e.g., quantitative investment strategies.'}, {'name': 'location', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The location of the study, e.g., US stock market.'}, {'name': 'count', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The number of papers to find.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'papers', 'description': 'A list of up to the specified count of academic papers.'}]}], ['InvestmentCaseStudy.analyze_investment_cases', {'name': 'InvestmentCaseStudy.analyze_investment_cases', 'description': 'This function analyzes investment cases based on specified companies and market.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'companies', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of company names to analyze investment cases for.'}, {'name': 'market', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The stock market where the companies operate, e.g., US.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'cases', 'description': 'Analyzed investment cases for the specified companies.'}]}], ['RegulationAuthority.get_current_regulations', {'name': 'RegulationAuthority.get_current_regulations', 'description': 'This function retrieves current regulations based on a topic and location.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'topic', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The topic of the regulations, e.g., quantitative investment.'}, {'name': 'location', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The location of the regulations, e.g., US.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'regulations', 'description': 'Current regulations for the specified topic and location.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `StockDataRetrieval.get_historical_data` 并传入 `market` 和 `duration`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "StockDataRetrieval.get_historical_data",
    "args": "{'market': 'US', 'duration': '5 years'}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
